snippet.title: MAIDEN & SPELL Demo Gameplay - Royal Arcanist Stage 2 - Hard Mode
snippet.description:
WEBSITE: https://www.mmkarigame.com
DEMO: https://mino-dev.itch.io/maidenandspelldemo

Young maidens seek adventure...

Maiden & Spell is a bullet hell battle game currently in development for PC!

Compete in local 1v1 bullet hell fights with your friends, or seek the truth of the Kingdom of Stars in the single-player Story Mode!

Features:  Cute characters!  Dazzling danmaku!  High difficulty!  Local multiplayer!  A fabulous soundtrack by the talented STEEL_PLUS!  日本語もありますよ！

PRESS KIT: https://www.mmkarigame.com/press-kit
DEVLOG: https://maidenspellgame.tumblr.com
MAILING LIST: https://mailchi.mp/2516536f5292/mino_dev

Created by 
mino_dev (Art, Design, Programming)
Twitter: https://twitter.com/mino_dev
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mino_dev/

steel_plus (Music)
Twitter: https://twitter.com/steel_plus
Bandcamp: https://steelplus.bandcamp.com
Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/steelplus

yichen (SFX)
Twitter: https://twitter.com/compressorphile
